<ab>Der stat czu Landshut </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> herczog
                                                  <expan>Heinr<ex>ich,</ex></expan> vormals von
                                                Cristan Wolczhofers, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
                                                burgers, <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wie
                                                man <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger bey ew czu
                                                Landshute in Urban
                                                  <expan>Fünfing<ex>er</ex>s</expan> herberg
                                                aufgehalten hab vier gancze und vier halbe tuche in
                                                  <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> groen ümbslag; und
                                                daz er <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tuch vor
                                                uns czu den heiligen behabt hab, daz die sein und
                                                  <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> sein, also daz khein
                                                auszman weder teil noch gemein daran hab; und haben
                                                auch sein gnade <expan>gebete<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz
                                                er <add>von <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan></add>
<add><expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan></add>
<expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wolt, daz dem
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> seine tuch wider
                                                würden. Nü ist der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> aber für uns
                                                  <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> und hat uns
                                                fürgelegt, wie daz im
                                                  <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> seine tuche noch
                                                niht wider worden sein.
                                                  <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                                  <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> durch
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günstige
                                                  <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gen dem
                                                  <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rczog</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich,</ex></expan> beweisen wöllet,
                                                daz <add>im</add>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> seine tuche noch
                                                  <expan>widerwerde<ex>n</ex></expan>. Als etc. Das
                                                  <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi post
                                                  <expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex>is</expan>
<expan>bap<ex>tis</ex><hi rend="sup">te</hi></expan>
                                                anno <expan>deci<ex>m</ex>o</expan>.</ab>
</div>
